  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Royce</b> is a family name and a given name in Westeros. People named <b>Royce</b> include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">House Royce</a>, a noble family of the Vale of Arryn</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Royce_Baratheon\" title=\"Royce Baratheon\">Royce Baratheon</a>, a Lord of Storm’s End</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Royce_Blackwood\" title=\"Royce Blackwood\">Royce Blackwood</a>, a son of Lord Blackwood during the reign of King Jaehaerys I Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Royce_II_Bolton\" title=\"Royce II Bolton\">Royce II Bolton</a>, a historical Red King</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Royce_IV_Bolton\" title=\"Royce IV Bolton\">Royce IV Bolton</a>, a historical Red King</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Royce_Caron\" title=\"Royce Caron\">Royce Caron</a>, a Lord of Nightsong</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Royce_Coldwater\" title=\"Royce Coldwater\">Royce Coldwater</a>, a Lord of Coldwater Burn</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404233424\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:13802-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404233424 and revision id 259308\n -->\n",
